org.objectstyle.cayenne.query
Interface Query

All Known Subinterfaces:
GenericSelectQuery, ParameterizedQuery
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractQuery, ProcedureQuery, SelectQuery, SqlSelectQuery, SQLTemplate
public interface Query

Defining a generic selecting or updating query that can be executed in Cayenne.

Author:
Andrei Adamchik
